PN,31601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,FResidents in a Yorkshire town have
OL,8,Fhigh levels of "forever chemicals",
OL,9,Fsome linked to cancer and other
OL,10,Fserious illnesses, in their blood, an
OL,11,FITV and ENDS Report investigation has
OL,12,Ffound.
OL,14,FITV's Exposure found that a third of
OL,15,Fresidents they tested in Bentham had
OL,16,Fhigh levels of PFAS chemicals in their
OL,17,Fbloodstreams.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,FPFAS are a group of millions of
OL,8,Fchemicals that are often described as
OL,9,Fforever chemicals because they take a
OL,10,Flong time to break down in the
OL,11,Fenvironment. Some of these chemicals
OL,12,Fare known and suspected carcinogens.
OL,14,FOne of these is PFOA, which has been
OL,15,Flinked to kidney and testicular cancer.
OL,17,FFor decades, Angus Fire, the main
OL,18,Femployer in Bentham, North Yorkshire,
OL,19,Froutinely manufactured and tested PFAS
OL,20,Ffirefighting foams that contained
OL,21,Ftraces of PFOA at its factory site.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,FResidents recall how test fires would
OL,8,Fbe set on the site, and the foam would
OL,9,Fbe used to put them out.
OL,11,F"I remember a siren going off, and
OL,12,Fthen not long after a big black plume
OL,13,Fof smoke", says Bentham local Angela
OL,14,FMcKinnell.
OL,16,F"Angus's had these steel vats and they
OL,17,Fset fire to them. That's when the
OL,18,Fsmoke would go. And then they'd put
OL,19,Fthem out with the extinguisher foam.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,F"We knew that not long after that,
OL,8,Fthere's going to be all this foam
OL,9,Flying about."
OL,11,FThe PFAS contamination on the site of
OL,12,Fthe factory in Bentham only came to
OL,13,Flight in 2024 after ENDS report
OL,14,Fjournalist Pippa Neill conducted a
OL,15,Fyear-long investigation.
OL,17,FShe obtained documents showing that
OL,18,Ftesting of groundwater on the Angus
OL,19,FFire site had revealed the highest
OL,20,Fknown concentrations of forever
OL,21,Fchemicals ever recorded in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,FThe testing was carried out by
OL,8,Fconsultants on behalf of Angus Fire in
OL,9,F2008.
OL,11,FDespite this and growing evidence that
OL,12,FPFOA caused harm to human health,
OL,13,FAngus continued to use the foam until
OL,14,F2016. It stopped producing PFAS foams
OL,15,Fin 2024.
OL,17,FEveryone who took part in ITV
OL,18,FExposure's blood testing lives within
OL,19,Fa kilometre of the factory or is a
OL,20,Fformer or current worker at Angus Fire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,FThe testing analysis was carried out
OL,8,Fby Eurofins Environment Testing in
OL,9,FSacramento, California. The results
OL,10,Frevealed for the first time the levels
OL,11,Fof the chemicals they had in their
OL,12,Fbloodstream.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,FIn the UK, there are no official
OL,8,Fguidelines on safe levels of PFAS in
OL,9,Fthe blood, so contributors were tested
OL,10,Fagainst NASEM standards, the
OL,11,Fscientific body that advises the U.S.
OL,12,Fgovernment.
OL,14,FIt says that PFAS levels of 2-20
OL,15,Fnanograms per millilitre of blood are
OL,16,Fassociated with the potential for
OL,17,Fadverse health effects. Those with
OL,18,Flevels above 20 would be at increased
OL,19,Frisk and are advised to have more
OL,20,Ffrequent health screenings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,FNine of the 39 people tested had PFAS
OL,8,Flevels above 20, putting them in the
OL,9,Fhighest risk category.
OL,11,FOne former worker at Angus Fire
OL,12,Frecorded a blood PFAS level of 405.
OL,13,FThis is over 200 times higher than the
OL,14,Flower risk threshold.
OL,16,FAngela McKinnell was one of the
OL,17,Fresidents tested. She had a level of
OL,18,F12 in her blood. Angela has a tumour
OL,19,Fin her kidney, and worries about the
OL,20,Fhealth of her neighbours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,F"All these people sort of our age, a
OL,8,Flittle bit older, little bit younger.
OL,9,Fwith cancer it's ridiculous, it's not
OL,10,Fnormal," she said.
OL,12,FRachel Harrison has lived in Bentham
OL,13,Fall her life. She has a level of 2 in
OL,14,Fher blood, but her toddler has a level
OL,15,Fof 10, while her baby showed a level
OL,16,Fof 13.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,F"I'm a bit shocked... I think I just
OL,8,Fdidn't want to think that the children
OL,9,Fwere affected by it. They might be
OL,10,Ffine. It might not affect their lives.
OL,11,FBut it might. It's hard to know what
OL,12,Fto do next".
OL,14,FDr David Megson, an expert in
OL,15,Fenvironmental forensics at Manchester
OL,16,FMetropolitan University, analysed the
OL,17,Fblood results for the programme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,FBecause no data is available for PFAS
OL,8,Flevels in blood across the UK, Dr
OL,9,FMegson compared the levels in Bentham
OL,10,Fwith the general population in the US.
OL,12,F"I was absolutely shocked when we
OL,13,Fstarted to run this data. Nearly
OL,14,Feverybody we tested was above average
OL,15,Fand two-thirds of them were in the top
OL,16,F5%," he said.
OL,18,F"A third of them were higher than
OL,19,Fanything we'd ever expect to see in
OL,20,Fthe background population.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,F"I've done a few contamination studies
OL,8,Fin my time as a scientist and I think
OL,9,Fthat this one is the one that stands
OL,10,Fout for just such a high proportion of
OL,11,Fpeople having elevated exposure of
OL,12,FPFAS. It was quite staggering."
OL,14,FIn a town meeting to address the
OL,15,Fproblem in June 2025, Angus Fire
OL,16,Ffailed to send a representative.
OL,18,FAngus Fire says it chose not to attend
OL,19,Fthe meeting to avoid overtaking the
OL,20,Fagenda.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,FThe company says it has always engaged
OL,8,Fopenly with the community in Bentham
OL,9,Fand elected representatives and that
OL,10,Fattendees were assured experts were
OL,11,Fundertaking work for Angus to provide
OL,12,Fanswers to their questions.
OL,14,FThe CEO of Angus Fire declined to be
OL,15,Finterviewed for the documentary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,FAngus Fire says it has always followed
OL,8,Flegal guidelines and that extensive
OL,9,F"containment" work has been carried
OL,10,Fout in recent years. It stresses that
OL,11,Four small sample is not proof of harm
OL,12,Fcaused by their actions.
OL,14,FBut for some residents, that is not
OL,15,Fenough to allay their fears. After a
OL,16,Flifetime in Bentham, Rachel has made
OL,17,Fthe difficult decision to leave her
OL,18,Fhometown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,F"If I have the opportunity to move my
OL,8,Fchildren away from something that
OL,9,Fwould cause them harm, you are going
OL,10,Fto do that."
OL,12,FAngus Fire says it has always followed
OL,13,Fguidelines as set out by the UK
OL,14,Fregulatory and health authorities and
OL,15,Fthey were only made aware of the
OL,16,Fpotentially harmful effects of PFAS
OL,17,Fand PFOA as industry and scientific
OL,18,Fknowledge grew and their understanding
OL,19,Fevolved at the same rate as that of
OL,20,Fregulators.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,FWatch In Our Blood: The Forever
OL,8,FChemicals Scandal on Sunday, March 22,
OL,9,Fat 22:15 on ITV or stream it on ITVX
OL,11,FIn response to the PFAS blood test
OL,12,Fresults in Bentham, Angus Fire says it
OL,13,Fis unfounded to classify the blood
OL,14,Fdata as high because the UK does not
OL,15,Fhave national blood PFAS guidance
OL,16,Fvalues, and the group tested was too
OL,17,Fsmall to draw conclusions about the
OL,18,Fwider Bentham community.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31617
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,FWhile it appreciates that these
OL,8,Ffindings may cause concern, Angus Fire
OL,9,Fsays having raised PFAS levels in
OL,10,Fblood is neither an indicator of
OL,11,Fhealth, nor of the way in which PFAS
OL,12,Fhas been absorbed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31618
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,FAt present, the understanding of the
OL,8,Fsite is insufficient to characterise
OL,9,Fthe land quality, but since 2024, it
OL,10,Fhas carried out significant
OL,11,Finvestigative, containment,
OL,12,Fcharacterisation, and remediation
OL,13,Fwork, including a stormwater treatment
OL,14,Fsystem that will reduce PFAS in
OL,15,Frainwater that runs off the site.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31619
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774048278
OL,3,CTests find high levels of toxic
OL,4,Cforever chemicals among Yorkshire town
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,FThe company says there is no
OL,8,Fdemonstrated causal link between the
OL,9,Fhistoric use of PFAS in the products
OL,10,Fhistorically manufactured by Angus
OL,11,FFire and any increased cancer rate in
OL,12,FBentham, and no regulator or health
OL,13,Fauthority has suggested otherwise.
OL,15,FFOR MORE INFORMATION, PLEASE VISIT:
OL,17,FEnvironment Agency
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
